<HL> Pepper...and Salt</HL>
<DD> 07/07/87</DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO>
<TEXT>
      Running Hazard
   Oh, joggers in
   The morning dews,
   Be careful of
   The path you choose,
   Lest (lost in fog)
   An evil fate
   Leads you onto
   The Interstate.
   --Robert Gordon. 

   ---
   Pain for Pay
   When life deals us blows
   That we can't overlook,
   Some suffer in silence
   And some write a book. 

   --E.B. de Vito. 

   ---
   Truth Capsule
   We never get a second chance to make a good first impression. 

   --B. Bader. 

</TEXT>
